urce initialization determines the mock usage.\n\n\n**Verifying AWS Environment State**\n\nI'm now carefully checking the conditions for DynamoDB seeding. It's critical that the process only proceeds if a valid AWS environment is configured. If not, the seeding process should be skipped and an informative message displayed. I'm confirming that the `backend/app/seed.py` is the single source for seeding and that there are no unexpected seeding scripts in other directories like `app/resources/developer-docs/`. I am double checking to make sure. I also need to review how user data and other relevant seed data are handled.\n\n\n"}}
